      "title": "\u2139\ufe0f About \u2014 BrainDead CubePart",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# \ud83e\udde0 BrainDead \u2014 CubePart Part Decomposition\n\nOpen-vocabulary, **part-controllable 3D**. Give CubePart a mesh + up to **8 part names** and it generates one clean mesh per part \u2014 ready for rigging / game engines.\n\n## Flow\n1. **BD Load Mesh** \u2014 pick a mesh (or set a file_path).\n2. **BD CubePart Segment** \u2014 type up to 8 comma/newline part names.\n3. **BD Mesh Preview (Thumbnails)** \u2014 labeled grid of every part (shown inline).\n4. **BD Preview 3D** \u2014 interactive, color-coded 3D viewer.\n5. **BD CubePart Get Part** \u2192 **BD Export Mesh With Colors**, named by **BD Save Context**.\n\n## Models (auto-download on first run)\n`Roblox/cubepart` + `Qwen/Qwen3-VL-4B-Instruct` \u2014 resolved via `extra_model_paths.yaml`. ~18 GB VRAM to load, ~70 s first run. Max **8** parts. Weights are CUBE3D **research-only** license \u2014 review before commercial use.\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)\n"
      ]
    },
